{"tid":387922,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"成日剃鬚剃損 有咩解決方法","createTime":"2017-09-05T04:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T13:37:46.000Z","uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54580f7eb80c6dafc821864d73584ce10ca1ad15","tid":387922,"uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"因為我鬚根粗 幾乎一日剃一次 但每次睇都會搞到兩邊腮位附近紅唒同有粒粒 想問下有咩解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n剃之前熱手巾 剃完之後再用凍毛巾敷 剃鬚膏  鬚後水咩方法都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1940cc8577c047cdbb8d79da0f70d065725539ee","tid":387922,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"剃鬚刀唔乾淨？"},{"pid":"c2629ae9e001bafa81c52faeafa1300c493edd86","tid":387922,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"用一排 電鬚刨先<br />\n等塊面生返好先"},{"pid":"31b6a8d16a4382d802e53e401abeb397bc880006","tid":387922,"uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剃鬚刀唔乾淨？</blockquote><br />\n用100度熱水浸過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f4a1451b2e26397bafe047b60da6de0c769fc6","tid":387922,"uid":142725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用一排 電鬚刨先<br />\n等塊面生返好先</blockquote><br />\n試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592439d1939755edb972a7084508330f8eb25082","tid":387922,"uid":116203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"鬚刨啦，冇咁易極傷塊面又快快手搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159a26a56c4380a5ece9e8ac8c76788e0779cbe0","tid":387922,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"買吉列隻5刀頭<br />\n電動=垃圾"},{"pid":"5f32045bf974e547e5b314d66720f24ad9b9d92c","tid":387922,"uid":67805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"「人中」同下唇邊位用剃刀；<br />\n其他位用眉鉗拔"},{"pid":"673264a0f9a7303e016ff109bd39797e6bedb622","tid":387922,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"通常我剃損都係因為刀片鈍左<br />\n試下換新刀片<br />\n<br />\n如果都唔得就換另一款刀片<br />\n總有一款啱你<br />\n<br />\n電鬚刨就懶人用<br />\n貪方便<br />\n但就無刀片剃得咁乾淨"},{"pid":"ee391be2726f88880e0dc69605bdde64da6c3fcb","tid":387922,"uid":62919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"剃鬚前，洗乾淨塊面前，跟住抹乾，再用熱水敷一敷，之後落剃鬚膏，樓主如果係敏感皮膚，可以用綠色果種剃鬚啫喱。<br />\n剃果陣唔好貪心，一下一下咁落，唔好連去幾下，剃幾刀有泡，就用水沖一沖；<br />\n剃完，凍水輕輕印一印，跟住再用鬚後水，最後搽埋保濕／面霜（如有用開）。<br />\n<br />\n番工既話，我都係一日剃一次，通常１星期至１０日就換剃鬚刀。<br />\n希望幫到樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe838733eafd5f9d80ac731357e128207a7256e4","tid":387922,"uid":104502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"如果無諗住留鬚 不如去做激光<br />\n長期剃搞到嗰個位啲皮膚差哂"},{"pid":"17667a99e6a22912c73cd9705c3cdd3c115c950c","tid":387922,"uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剃鬚前，洗乾淨塊面前，跟住抹乾，再用熱水敷一敷，之後落剃鬚膏，樓主如果係敏感皮膚，可以用綠色果種剃鬚啫喱。<br />\n剃果陣唔好貪心，一下一下咁落，唔好連去幾下，剃幾刀有泡，就用水沖一沖；<br />\n剃完，凍水輕輕印一印，跟住再用鬚後水，最後搽埋保濕／面霜（如有用開）。<br />\n<br />\n番工既話，我都係一日剃一次，通常１星期至１０日就換剃鬚刀。<br />\n希望幫到樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試下 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734e4ee8d1a81db5eea5da87b10c776c7fcbdd1e","tid":387922,"uid":130559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"留鬚都係潮流"}]}